Getting hitched in a beautiful resort or luxurious hotel is something that every bride dreams off. Be it a small party venue or a spacious banquet hall WMG has a plethora of wedding venues to offer to their lovebirds who are thinking of getting married. You might not realize it but the first and foremost thing when your wedding dates are out is to start hunting venues that fits with your budget and that too, which is near to your locality.


Be it a destination wedding in Jaipur or Goa we have 1000s of options available for you to select your dream-wedding venue for your most special day of life. Whether you want a poolside venue for your mehendi function or a lawn for cocktail party WedMeGood is your wedding planning app and website wherein you can select multiple wedding vendors for your celebrations and wedding day.


What are the things to ensure while booking your wedding venue?

We all know that a good amount of money goes when we select a venue for a wedding. Many couples think to book other vendors like caterers, decorators, planners, etc. but end up realizing that many hotels and resorts also have their in-house services and team to offer to their couples. Brides! Whether you are looking for a farmhouse for your reception party or an affordable hotel for a destination wedding ensure that you follow the pointers while booking your wedding venue, which are as follows:

  • Budget: We know that you must be having a restricted budget because getting married in Indian is an expensive thing. However, worry not! We advise you to always remain to your budget and start finding the best wedding venues that matches your budget yet have good services and wedding banquet halls to offer for your wedding.
  • Locality: If you are having your wedding in your city then we advise you to select your wedding venue that is close to your area. However, if you are planning for a destination wedding then, make sure that you do a thorough research about the hotel or resort, looking at their website and social media links; dig in their property images such as their rooms, washrooms and banquet space.
  • Services: Well, services are something that everyone wants to know. Be it a 24*7 room service or well equipped with modern amenities or some lip smacking dishes do research on their services and total rooms available.
  • Banquet space: Now, this is where you will take your wedding vows so ensure is perfect for your wedding. Make a guest list and see how many people you are inviting. According to your list start digging and see if the venues have the banquet halls matching with your criteria.
  • In-house: We often might forget this point but many hotels and resorts also have their in-house services like In-house dcor, DJ, caterers and planners too. So, in case if you are planning to book a wedding venue for your celebrations then, ensure to ask them about their in-house services as they offer discounts to their clients.
  • Payment procedure: Lastly, ask about their payment procedure as to how much advance do they expect before and after the wedding.

Well, this all seems too much, right? However, when it comes to wedding venue nobody can compromise because if you select a good hotel or resort that provides you with the services you need, you will sure shot have an unforgettable experience or else, a bad venue can surely spoil your function, mood and money.


Apart from wedding venues, you can easily find wedding photographer, bridal makeup artists, decorators for your wedding, wedding planners and more. You can easily check out the pictures, reviews & ratings, shortlist and contact vendors directly. You can also download WedMeGoods Wedding planning app on Android & iOS and plan on the go.
